author: The Current
description:
David Rawlings describes the 1935 guitar he found in a basement
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Singer-songwriter David Rawlings talks about his 1935 Epiphone Olympic guitar, which he found covered in dust in a friend’s basement — and then located an incredible item to trade for it.

Credits
Guest – @davidrawlings 
Producer – Mike Pengra
Video Director – Evan Clark
Camera Operators – Evan Clark, Josh Sauvageau
Audio Mix – Cameron Wiley

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full three-song session of The xx, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2017.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Say Something Loving
00:04:22 I Dare You
00:08:34 On Hold

Musicians
Romy Madley Croft – guitar, vocals
Oliver Sim – bass guitar, vocals
Jamie xx – beats, programming and percussion
